      <title>12张图表解释了习近平领导下的中国如何变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/xi-s-biggest-wins-and-losses-after-more-than-a-decade-in-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2012年接任国家主席以来，中国国家主席习近平所拥有的个人权力达到了几十年来从未有过的程度。这也意味着他比以往任何时候都更有责任实现国家设定的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/xi-s-biggest-wins-and-losses-after-more-than-a-decade-in-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
