    <item>
      <title>台湾警告中国可能加大对新政府的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/taiwan-warns-china-likely-to-increase-pressure-on-new-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台北的一名高级国家安全官员周一警告称，在台湾五月份向新政府移交权力之前和之后，中国可能会加大对台湾的施压力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/taiwan-warns-china-likely-to-increase-pressure-on-new-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 05:34:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过修改法律巩固执政党对内阁的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/china-to-cement-communist-party-grip-on-cabinet-with-law-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国立法机关投票修改了一项已有四年历史的法律，从而加强了共产党对内阁的控制，凸显了习近平主席让共产党控制政府所有主要杠杆的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/china-to-cement-communist-party-grip-on-cabinet-with-law-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 04:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
